{"tid":836674,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯在聯賽盃出局摩連奴指新制不利強隊","createTime":"2018-09-25T22:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T12:04:07.000Z","uid":12006,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9842c4778aecf33762c327ae66e602b681aaeda8","tid":836674,"uid":12006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T22:36:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關曼連咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 曼連係強隊咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n英格蘭聯賽盃第三圈賽事，曼聯在法定時間2:2迫和冠聯的打比郡，但互射12碼輸7:8，被林柏特執教的打比郡淘汰。曼聯在開賽初段就領先，由馬達在上半場3分鐘取得入球。換邊後形勢逆轉，曼聯被追和，並有門將羅美路領紅牌出場，以眾凌寡的打比郡再入一球，曼聯到補時階段最後1分鐘，由費蘭尼頭槌扳平2比2，要互射12碼決勝負。雙方頭五輪全部射入，到突然死亡階段，菲爾鍾斯在第8輪射失，曼聯無緣再晉一級。<br />\n<br />\n林柏特賽後說對球隊表現感到驕傲。摩連奴就說，聯賽盃改制和波後直接踢十二碼是對強隊不利，如果有30分鐘加時，強隊通常都可以勝出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1032329&amp;csid=261_369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1032329%26csid%3D261_369&d=QPh9qvvmeiGxVTY%2FFfJyqgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8bd72f4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1032329&amp;csid=261_369</a>"},{"pid":"214f281c247f9565ca1953e03bc262f67a6cc74a","tid":836674,"uid":3342,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:04:04.000Z","msg":"屌你主場都不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb4241180d445966ae73079031984f7de7b2314","tid":836674,"uid":24412,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:09:14.000Z","msg":"摩三季<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a145128f007baf722338498225fb9abb8d0a2e","tid":836674,"uid":12006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be50dd583d418531dd6d9a5ab85b35595f06cf2","tid":836674,"uid":74272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c82e86c523255c3a27b570915bb98ee8e8a6fb","tid":836674,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9625f5506ccf6e55eea21202edb874209cdfdc8e","tid":836674,"uid":34772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:22:14.000Z","msg":"Harry Wilson <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77d8b60068c59439e78cb44378320ca1a2815f1","tid":836674,"uid":69680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"請尊重，謝謝"},{"pid":"ce76e95facc70239b98171cf374c409f58dff9c3","tid":836674,"uid":8883,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:45:15.000Z","msg":"英聯盃和波即射12碼 摩佬：咁先正<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/836669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/836669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7a0a1bd58da8022d224b3b17cf1ec5f73b20c9e2","tid":836674,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/084545_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F084545_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=60a1aad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6225fa73c2d0b3d590c4fb61b6ef2473d26120cb","tid":836674,"uid":45428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:46:15.000Z","msg":"英聯盃第三圈爆出驚天大冷，曼聯主場先開紀錄下，竟然要到補時先逼和英冠仔打比郡2:2，不過去到互射12碼一樣要輸，菲爾鍾斯宴客變出局罪人。賽後領隊莫連奴批評球隊，不斷浪費入球機會而致未能「殺死」比賽，矛頭直指於上半場，無論單刀同空龍都唔入嘅盧卡古。<br />\n<br />\n「我哋有機會入波時，就偏偏射唔入，上半場我哋有大把機會，曼聯絕對有權『殺死』場波。半場於更衣室，我講番上場聯賽（對狼隊，最後被追成1:1完場）一樣嘅說話，我哋一定識得將場波擺入雪櫃。我哋做唔到，下半場就未能控制大局。我希望隊波可以主動啲，於羅美路領紅後球隊遇到困難，不過曼聯依然努力不懈，我哋堅持到最後一秒。」<br />\n<br />\n「其實我哋賽前有練12碼，當我見到球隊射入頭6輪，就知會有麻煩，因為要到菲爾鍾斯同艾歷拜利射。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼聯早前於英超被升班球隊狼隊逼和，寸王又面臨巨大壓力，陣中球霸保羅普巴，公開質疑領隊莫連奴戰術，話佢係曼聯未能於奧脫福「進攻進攻再進攻」嘅罪魁禍首。寸王一向係方丈，得罪方丈當然唔會有好結果，英媒BBC爆料，話莫連奴於操練時，當住全場球員面前表示普巴以後唔會再做曼聯隊長，同呢位法國世界盃功臣正式決裂！<br />\n<br />\n普巴早前表示，曼聯於主場打唔出威勢，未能整場賽事壓住對手嚟攻，當記者問佢邊個令到班波咁，佢就話：「唔可以講出口，因為我只係個球員，總之就唔係我啦。」雖然冇開名，但咁樣同公開插寸王完全冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n英國多間傳媒，包括公信力一流嘅BBC都有報道，話莫連奴已經向普巴大報復。日前球隊於訓練場操練後，佢向全隊作出訓話，當住全部球員表示「冇一個個別球員係大過曼聯」，直斥普巴言論不當，另外對狼隊一戰，亦都係普巴掛住演嘢扭失波、導致球隊被追和嘅罪人，所以已決定唔會再畀普巴當上隊長一職。本季正隊長路爾斯華倫西亞有傷在身，普巴曾3次帶上紅魔隊長臂章落場。到今仗英聯盃對打比郡，普巴被收起冇得落場，但後者今仗文裝一度於看台睇波，同隊友有講有笑，心情似乎冇受影響，可能寸王愈憎自己、自己離隊機會愈高，或者反而更合普巴心意。<br />\n<br />\n普巴冇得再做隊長，當華倫西亞又缺陣時，基斯史摩寧、安達靴里拉、尼曼查馬迪、艾舒利楊格都係隊長候選人，其中楊格就於對打比一仗做隊長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普巴係鬼盧卡古又係鬼<br />\n摩三季<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716444aa5824d5443fcfb22b6c033d415db9d5dd","tid":836674,"uid":60807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"個頭先話即刻射12碼會有利 特別對有歐洲賽事兼顧嘅球隊<br />\n<br />\n呢刻又話不利 真係巴士任你擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f389ec140920ef8a244ab0b76258eaeaa950c541","tid":836674,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:54:46.000Z","msg":"點解射12碼對強隊不利？"},{"pid":"ff3c45dfd6d4b70b06698906d49559bd6b589fbc","tid":836674,"uid":141623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:55:31.000Z","msg":"佢下下話輸波唔係自己戰術有問題，係球員問題<br />\n<br />\n我係球員都憎你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd高層唔係盲既，再咁落去遲早玩死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5decbaff8fdeb1732dce1122c6e31f48bfff0342","tid":836674,"uid":148224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"716444aa5824d5443fcfb22b6c033d415db9d5dd","tid":836674,"uid":60807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"個頭先話即刻射12碼會有利 特別對有歐洲賽事兼顧嘅球隊<br />\n<br />\n呢刻又話不利 真係巴士任你擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"精神分裂就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13da6eec681cd3703e2436123ac3ffe84aeeccfd","tid":836674,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5decbaff8fdeb1732dce1122c6e31f48bfff0342","tid":836674,"uid":148224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"716444aa5824d5443fcfb22b6c033d415db9d5dd","tid":836674,"uid":60807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"個頭先話即刻射12碼會有利 特別對有歐洲賽事兼顧嘅球隊<br />\n<br />\n呢刻又話不利 真係巴士任你擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"精神分裂就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"公我嬴字你輸是常識"},{"pid":"3466d5ed4874eb6c1aec8d67060086eca8f17154","tid":836674,"uid":2899,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:14:59.000Z","msg":"依家俾個下台階你咪幾好<br />\n輸十二碼都有得賴下有運氣成份<br />\n再踢多三十分鐘 我驚你都輸埋咋踢到咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/091305_aa72b52c0ad76c9bc3fdcd6cb3ce59e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F091305_aa72b52c0ad76c9bc3fdcd6cb3ce59e7.jpg&h=ae4f105e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca231f93e6af7bd124e7a92533a607d42a6fe9ce","tid":836674,"uid":32486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:17:45.000Z","msg":"我地曼自搵自洗 + c朗個筆未洗完<br />\n錢對我地只係數字<br />\n買起你成隊打比郡都仲得"},{"pid":"e16663649d52917614fdd7eb09c9018d9fcf7988","tid":836674,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918ce4a9c06bac6a1fb16b31a9a18c55d8c07b23","tid":836674,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e16663649d52917614fdd7eb09c9018d9fcf7988","tid":836674,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:24:46.000Z","msg":"創意啦"},{"pid":"377a9a888c65a3dcdd482cdb444ece790a9f9c82","tid":836674,"uid":124020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"918ce4a9c06bac6a1fb16b31a9a18c55d8c07b23","tid":836674,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e16663649d52917614fdd7eb09c9018d9fcf7988","tid":836674,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:24:02.000Z"